<div class="content-area cell large-5 large-order-3 xxlarge-4">

  <h1 class="header-xlarge">Data</h1>

  <p>NYC Street Map currently provides the following information:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Boundaries of mapped and unmapped streets</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Official names of streets</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Mapped street widths</strong> <small>(usually includes sidewalks)</small></li>
    <li><strong>Alteration maps showing approved changes to the City Map since 1938</strong> <small>(in some areas, maps are available that show changes which have been approved by the City Planning Commission and City Council, but have not yet taken effect)</small></li>
    <li><strong>Street and place names established by local law</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <p class="text-small"><em>This app will be updated as more information becomes electronically available.</em></p>

  <hr>

  <h2 class="header-xlarge">Data Sources</h2>

  <ul>
    {{#each model as |source|}}
      <li>
        <p>
          {{#if source.meta.description}}
            <span style="display:block;" class="dark-gray"><strong>{{source.meta.description}}</strong></span>
          {{/if}}
          {{#if source.meta.url}}
            {{#each source.meta.url as |url|}}
              <span style="display:block;" class="no-margin"><a href="{{url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{fa-icon 'external-link-alt'}} {{url}}</a></span>
            {{/each}}
          {{/if}}
          {{#if source.meta.updated_at}}
            <span style="display:block;" class="dark-gray text-small">Updated: {{source.meta.updated_at}}</span>
          {{/if}}
        </p>
      </li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>

  <p>For more information on the licenses which govern OpenStreetMap, please refer to <a href="www.openstreetmap.org/copyright">www.openstreetmap.org/copyright</a></p>


  {{outlet}}
</div>
